dc_title_s: Audubon, Camden County, New Jersey : including Oaklyn and parts of Haddon Township (Sheet 18)
dc_description_s: "Aug. 1930." Includes location map, key, streets and specials index, and text. North oriented towards upper left. "4950." Historic Maps copy has sheets 1-3, 6-9, 12-13, 15 and 17-19; sheets 4-5 and 20, showing Haddon Township, and sheets 10-11 and 16, showing Oaklyn, foldered separately.
dc_publisher_s: New York : Sanborn Map Company, 1930, c1931.
